'''法尔达电台'''（{{lang-fa|رادیو فردا}}，{{lang-en|Radio Farda}}，又译作“'''法达电台'''”，意译为“'''明日电台'''”<ref>{{cite web |url=http://news.cctv.com/world/20070527/100313.shtml |title=伊朗声称破获数个西方间谍团伙 |author=关新 |agency=中国新闻网 |publisher=央视网 |accessdate=2016-11-02 |date=2007-05-27 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20161102023349/http://news.cctv.com/world/20070527/100313.shtml |archivedate=2016-11-02 |deadurl=yes }}</ref>），是一家接受[[美国|美国]]官方资助、专门针对[[伊朗|伊朗]]广播的电台<ref>{{cite web |url=http://news.cctv.com/world/20070205/102684.shtml |title=以特工暗杀伊朗顶尖核专家？ |agency=新华社 |newspaper=成都商报 |publisher=央视网 |accessdate=2016-11-02 |date=2007-02-05 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20070206203316/http://news.cctv.com/world/20070205/102684.shtml |archivedate=2007-02-06 |deadurl=yes }}</ref>，为[[自由欧洲电台/自由电台|自由欧洲电台/自由电台]]（RFE/RL）的分台，总部位于[[捷克|捷克]][[布拉格|布拉格]]<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.broadcastingcable.com/news/washington/radio-free-europeradio-liberty-videographer-injured/160608 |title=Radio Free Europe/Radio Liberty Videographer Injured |newspaper= |publisher=Broadcasting & Cable |accessdate=2016-11-02 |date=2016-10-24 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20161102022652/http://www.broadcastingcable.com/news/washington/radio-free-europeradio-liberty-videographer-injured/160608 |archivedate=2016-11-02 |deadurl=yes }}</ref>。法尔达电台每天24小时通过短波、卫星及互联网，使用[[波斯语|波斯语]]向伊朗播出。

==概要==
法尔达电台的前身为1998年开播的自由欧洲电台/自由电台波斯语广播，2002年12月改为现名<ref>{{cite book|title=国家传播战略|url=https://books.google.com.hk/books?id=N3jXl_MsvhsC|author=臧具林, 陈卫星|publisher=中国传媒大学出版社|year=2011|page=172|accessdate=2016-11-02|isbn=9787565701801|archive-date=2019-05-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190520120056/https://books.google.com.hk/books?id=N3jXl_MsvhsC|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.rferl.org/p/5796.html |title=RFE/RL History |newspaper= |publisher=RFE/RL |accessdate=2016-11-02 |date= |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20161017230443/http://www.rferl.org/p/5796.html |archivedate=2016-10-17 |deadurl=yes }}</ref>。法尔达电台成立之后，曾长期由RFE/RL和[[美国之音|美国之音]]（VOA）共同运营<ref>{{cite web |url=http://iipdigital.usembassy.gov/st/chinese/article/2008/01/20080122152558esnamfuak0.3600122.html#axzz4OolMF7cH |title=五大国际广播机构共同谴责对新闻自由的威胁 |author=Stephen Kaufman |newspaper= |publisher=美国参考 |accessdate=2016-11-02 |date=2008-01-18 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20161102033152/http://iipdigital.usembassy.gov/st/chinese/article/2008/01/20080122152558esnamfuak0.3600122.html#axzz4OolMF7cH |archivedate=2016-11-02 |deadurl=yes }}</ref>，从2008年7月7日起，美国[[广播理事会|广播理事会]]（BBG）将其完全纳入RFE/RL旗下<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.rferl.org/info/Iran/186.html |title=RADIO FARDA |newspaper= |publisher=RFE/RL |accessdate=2016-11-02 |date= |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20080731141217/http://www.rferl.org/info/Iran/186.html |archivedate=2008-07-31 |deadurl=yes }}</ref>。法尔达电台自称“极少数向伊朗人民提供未经审查消息的媒体之一”<ref name="bbg131107">{{cite web |url=https://www.bbg.gov/2013/11/07/rferls-radio-farda-and-radio-free-afghanistan-honored-by-aib/ |title=RFE/RL's Radio Farda and Radio Free Afghanistan Honored By AIB |newspaper= |publisher=BBG |accessdate=2016-11-02 |date=2013-11-07 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20161102061518/https://www.bbg.gov/2013/11/07/rferls-radio-farda-and-radio-free-afghanistan-honored-by-aib/ |archivedate=2016-11-02 |deadurl=yes }}</ref>，每周7天、每天24小时通过设在[[德国|德国]]、[[阿联酋|阿联酋]]和[[斯里兰卡|斯里兰卡]]的发射站向伊朗播出政治、文化和经济新闻以及体育、西方音乐和波斯音乐等节目。除无线电广播外，听众也可通过卫星及互联网收听法尔达电台的节目。另外，该台还开办了针对伊朗播出的电视节目<ref name="bbg160420">{{cite web |url=https://www.bbg.gov/2016/04/20/radio-fardas-tv-signal-jammed-tehran/ |title=Radio Farda's TV signal jammed in Tehran |newspaper= |publisher=BBG |accessdate=2016-11-02 |date=2016-04-20 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20161102055754/https://www.bbg.gov/2016/04/20/radio-fardas-tv-signal-jammed-tehran/ |archivedate=2016-11-02 |deadurl=yes }}</ref>。据BBG宣称，每周约有300万伊朗人收听法尔达电台的节目，电台网页每月浏览量达到1000万人次<ref name="bbg131107"/><ref name="bbg130130">{{cite web |url=https://www.bbg.gov/2013/01/30/cyber-attacks-target-radio-farda-journalists/ |title=Cyber Attacks Target Radio Farda Journalists |newspaper= |publisher=BBG |accessdate=2016-11-02 |date=2013-01-30 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20161102060636/https://www.bbg.gov/2013/01/30/cyber-attacks-target-radio-farda-journalists/ |archivedate=2016-11-02 |deadurl=yes }}</ref>。

2009年7月，[[美国国会|美国国会]]通过了“伊朗审查制度受害者法案”，并据此拨款3000万美元，资助RFE/RL、VOA和法尔达电台用波斯语向伊朗广播<ref>{{cite journal |url=http://www.haixia-info.com/articles/6682.html |2= |title=《較量無聲》紀錄片全文（三） |author=编辑部整理 |newspaper= |publisher= |journal=海峡评论 |accessdate=2016-11-02 |year=2014 |issue=4 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20161102040207/http://www.haixia-info.com/articles/6682.html |archivedate=2016-11-02 |deadurl=yes }}</ref>；这一年，法尔达电台的[[簡訊|-{zh-cn:短信;zh-hk:短訊;zh-tw:簡訊;zh-sg:简讯;}-]]服务上线，[[Facebook|Facebook]]、[[Twitter|Twitter]]页面也同时开通，截至2016年4月，其Facebook页面关注人数已突破150万<ref name="bbg160420"/>。

2009年6月开始，伊朗爆发大规模[[伊朗綠色革命|反政府示威]]，法尔达电台也与[[BBC|BBC]]、VOA等西方国家广播电视机构的波斯语频道一样，被伊朗政府干扰<ref name="bbg160420"/><ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.rferl.org/content/Iranian_Government_Steps_Up_Jamming_of_Radio_Farda/1763761.html |title=Iranian Government Steps Up Jamming of Radio Farda |author=Charles Recknagel |newspaper= |publisher=RFE/RL |accessdate=2016-11-02 |date=2009-06-26 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160304060829/http://www.rferl.org/content/Iranian_Government_Steps_Up_Jamming_of_Radio_Farda/1763761.html |archivedate=2016-03-04 |deadurl=yes }}</ref>。然而与BBC、VOA等“英美喉舌”不同，法尔达电台开播后的一段时间，伊朗官方对其采取了容忍的态度（虽然期间也有记者被扣押或被捕）<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.csmonitor.com/World/Middle-East/2010/0210/Iran-widens-journalist-crackdown-before-demonstrations |title=Iran widens journalist crackdown before demonstrations |newspaper=Christian Science Monitor |author=Iason Athanasiadis |publisher= |accessdate=2016-11-02 |date=2010-02-10 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160304054321/http://www.csmonitor.com/World/Middle-East/2010/0210/Iran-widens-journalist-crackdown-before-demonstrations |archivedate=2016-03-04 |deadurl=yes }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.nytimes.com/2007/09/05/world/middleeast/05tehran.html |title=Iran Permits Journalist to Go |newspaper=New York Times |author= |publisher= |accessdate=2016-11-02 |date=2007-09-05 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20150605040757/http://www.nytimes.com/2007/09/05/world/middleeast/05tehran.html |archivedate=2015-06-05 |deadurl=yes }}</ref>。但在2010年2月，伊朗逮捕了七名法尔达电台的工作人员，并指控其中一些人为美国间谍机构工作，并涉嫌在2009年的反政府暴力示威中煽动抗议者<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.voachinese.com/a/iran-radio-20100208-83781147/461143.html |title=伊朗称逮捕7名与美资电台有关人员 |author= |newspaper= |publisher=VOA |accessdate=2016-11-02 |date=2010-02-08 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20161102053448/http://www.voachinese.com/a/iran-radio-20100208-83781147/461143.html |archivedate=2016-11-02 |deadurl=yes }}</ref>。法尔达电台的记者曾遭到网络[[黑客|黑客]]攻击<ref name="bbg130130"/>，电台工作人员在伊朗国内的家人也不时受到审问和滋扰<ref name="bbg160420"/>。

